snippet.title: Everything You Need to Know About Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's CRAZY Relationship and Court Battle
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have had a tumultuous relationship to say the least. They started dating in 2012, got married in February 2015, and had their divorce finalized in January 2017.


Amber initially filed for divorce in 2016 and got a temporary restraining order against him, citing “physical abuse.” Then there were photos of Amber with bruises and the world had officially canceled Johnny at that point.


In this video, we run through 5 insane facts about Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's Relationship & their court case battle. These are facts that are often overlooked... especially the last one where Elon Musk comes into play. #johnnydepp #amberheard #elonmusk
